Over the past month, I have done many podcasts from my home office in Jackson.  Each one has been different, and my hope is that my story has helped others half as much as it has helped me through sharing it and going deep with the various hosts. On the following podcasts we have covered why I left TOMS and started Madefor, how I have used the enneagram to understand myself better, why the Hoffman Process is the greatest gift we can give to ourselves, how psychedelics could be the future of medicine with regard to mental health, my divorce and the conscious uncoupling program that brought us both great healing, morning practices and other methods I use daily for grounding and connection to God, and so much more.....so if any of this resonates with you, here is the list of podcasts I have recently been on and are so grateful for, most can also be found in highlights:
@timferriss 
