Excited to share that our So iLL X TOMS collection is finally here! 
@TOMS and @SoiLL partnered to create rock climbing shoes and rock climbing inspired limited-edition slip-ons. 
TOMS and So iLL, together with @1Climb_Official, a nonprofit dedicated to introducing 100,000 kids to climbing, helped build a climbing wall at the Boys and Girls Club of Los Angeles.
